{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found durable pitch tables and some stage plumbing already in place, which means this task is mostly about wiring the actual generation pipeline, selection flow, and main-pane rendering into the existing session architecture. I\u2019m readi...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_4", "text": "I found durable pitch tables and some stage plumbing already in place, which means this task is mostly about wiring the actual generation pipeline, selection flow, and main-pane rendering into the existing session architecture. I\u2019m reading the visual-QA skill and the current session/pitch code paths next so I can reuse the repo\u2019s patterns instead of adding a one-off feature slice.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 11, "prompt_index": 45, "prompt_name": "44 \u2014 Story Pitch Generation Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:50:37-07:00"}
