{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The session snapshot currently exposes only `selected_pitch`, so resuming old pitch sets would be impossible in the UI even if rows existed. I\u2019m validating that assumption against the front-end types and the existing AI-adapter pattern n...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_23", "text": "The session snapshot currently exposes only `selected_pitch`, so resuming old pitch sets would be impossible in the UI even if rows existed. I\u2019m validating that assumption against the front-end types and the existing AI-adapter pattern now, then I\u2019ll add the missing data contract and generation endpoint in one pass.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 46, "prompt_index": 45, "prompt_name": "44 \u2014 Story Pitch Generation Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:51:13-07:00"}
