{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I confirmed the prompt itself expects a real generation service, not just stage-state toggling. I\u2019m tracing the worker/job path now because the repo already treats pitch generation as a background story tool, and that\u2019s the cleanest plac...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_34", "text": "I confirmed the prompt itself expects a real generation service, not just stage-state toggling. I\u2019m tracing the worker/job path now because the repo already treats pitch generation as a background story tool, and that\u2019s the cleanest place to make generation durable and resumable.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 66, "prompt_index": 45, "prompt_name": "44 \u2014 Story Pitch Generation Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T20:51:33-07:00"}
