{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The compose stack is already up, but the repo\u2019s compose entrypoint is not `docker compose` from the root. This project routes through `./scripts/dev-compose.sh`, and the live frontend is on `http://localhost:8566`; I\u2019m using that path fo...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_198", "text": "The compose stack is already up, but the repo\u2019s compose entrypoint is not `docker compose` from the root. This project routes through `./scripts/dev-compose.sh`, and the live frontend is on `http://localhost:8566`; I\u2019m using that path for the browser checks instead of the skill\u2019s default port assumptions.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 365, "prompt_index": 45, "prompt_name": "44 \u2014 Story Pitch Generation Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T21:18:43-07:00"}
