{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the pitch generation pipeline end to end and committed the product changes on the current branch as `d3b4ece` with message `feat(prompt-44): pitch generation pipeline`. The backend now has a dedicated pitch-generation adapter...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_266", "text": "Implemented the pitch generation pipeline end to end and committed the product changes on the current branch as `d3b4ece` with message `feat(prompt-44): pitch generation pipeline`.\n\nThe backend now has a dedicated pitch-generation adapter/service stack with quality evaluation and heuristic fallback, durable batch persistence in session hydration, explicit generation and selection endpoints, and story-tool integration. The frontend now renders a real pitch stage with generation controls, comparison cards, batch history, selection handling, and chat echoes for generated pitch batches. The required reviewer summary was written last to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/44_story_pitch_generation_pipeline/summary.md).\n\nVerification completed:\n- Backend: Ruff check passed; touched backend files passed `ruff format --check`; targeted pytest matrix passed `55 passed`.\n- Frontend: targeted workspace test passed `18 passed`; ESLint passed; production build passed.\n- Browser QA: real compose-backed session generated 4 durable pitch cards and reloaded with 4 `Choose pitch` buttons still present on both desktop and mobile. Screenshots were captured under `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/`, including `prompt-44-pitches-desktop-stage.png` and `prompt-44-pitches-mobile-stage.png`.\n- Repo-wide `make check`: still fails on unrelated pre-existing backend formatting drift outside this prompt\u2019s diff; that limitation is documented in the summary.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 484, "prompt_index": 45, "prompt_name": "44 \u2014 Story Pitch Generation Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T21:26:11-07:00"}
